title: Nucleus 的back权限问题
author: 凄惨世界
txt_content:
backnucleus.back.baseADMINAllows the user to run the command /backbacknucleus.back.exempt.cooldownADMINAllows the user to bypass the cooldown for /backbacknucleus.back.exempt.costADMINAllows the user to bypass the cost for /backbacknucleus.back.exempt.warmupADMINAllows the user to bypass the warmup for /backbacknucleus.back.targets.deathUSERSets the player's /back location on deathbacknucleus.back.targets.portalUSERSets the player's /back location on portal teleports.backnucleus.back.targets.teleportUSERSets the player's /back location on returnable teleports.这些权限都给了
插件用的是最新的附属也是最新的api7也没有问题
版本：1.12.2
但是玩家就是不能使用back
